        <track>Open Mobile Linux Devroom</track>
        <type></type>
        <language></language>
        <abstract>Buildroot is a nice, simple and efficient tool to build small to medium sized embedded Linux systems. It to automates the process of building a cross-compiling toolchain, the root filesystem with all userspace components, a Linux kernel image and a bootloader image.  It is used for embedded systems ranging from industrial controllers to hand-held media devices.</abstract>
