        <title>Welcome</title>
        <subtitle></subtitle>
        <track>Ada Devroom</track>
        <type></type>
        <language></language>
        <abstract>Welcome to the Ada Developer Room at FOSDEM 2012, which is organized by Ada-Belgium in cooperation with Ada-Europe.</abstract>
        <description>Ada-Belgium and Ada-Europe are both non-profit organizations set to promote the use of Ada, and to disseminate the knowledge of it into academic, research and industrial establishments in Belgium and Europe, resp. Ada-Europe has member-organizations, such as Ada-Belgium, in various countries.

More information on this event is available on the Ada-Belgium web-site (see link).</description>
        <persons>
          <person id="581"></person>
        </persons>
        <links>
          <link href="http://www.cs.kuleuven.be/~dirk/ada-belgium/events/12/120204-fosdem.html">Ada Developer Room at FOSDEM 2012</link>
