        <duration>00:25</duration>
        <room>H.1309</room>
        <slug>vrit_db</slug>
        <title>Virtualized Databases</title>
        <subtitle></subtitle>
        <track>MySQL and Friends Devroom</track>
        <type></type>
        <language></language>
        <abstract>Let's have a look at the why and how of virtualization and see how it impacts applications with a big hunger for resources. We will run through the different layers of a virtualized environment and examine their impact. Can we tune MySQL to be better adapted to a virtual environment?</abstract>
