        <abstract>Percona Toolkit is an indispensable set of opensource command-line tools for managing and administering MySQL servers. This session will introduce the toolkit and the available tools, then demonstrate how to use some of the tools to manage replication, analyze queries, perform common DBA tasks, analyze disk I/O usage, and more.</abstract>
